          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Stop wrestling with payroll spreadsheets and manual journal entries. Our seamless integration automates everything, keeps you compliant, and gives you real-time visibility into payroll expenses.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/contact" class="bg-orange-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-orange-700 transition-colors">
              Get Integration Assessment
            </a>
            <a href="/pricing" class="border-2 border-orange-600 text-orange-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-orange-50 transition-colors">
              View Integration Plans
            </a>
